                            <p><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2 text-warning"></i><strong>Multas:</strong> $1,000 por d√≠a de retraso</p>
                            <p class="mb-0"><i class="fas fa-phone me-2 text-info"></i><strong>Contacto:</strong> biblioteca@adso.edu.co</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                            <h5 class="mb-0">
